    - Perfect, thank you. I'll wait here.
    - Uhm okay
  - text: Hello! One pickle taco, please.
    options:
    - I'll make it for you straigh away, just hold on for a minute
    - No sorry
    responses:
    - Perfect, thank you. I'll wait here.
    - Uhm okay
  eatingMessage: 'The customer finishes the taco and storms out, in tears.  '
